channel.title: DePulse Errors
channel.description:
So, I just downloaded the DePulse Source and Client, and usually, by habit, I compile it first to check for errors, and this time, I got a few, and I can't figure them out. Any help?
Errors; [code].\server.java:50: cannot find symbol symbol : class FightCaves location: class server public static FightCaves FightCaves = null; ^ .\server.java:116: cannot find symbol symbol : class FightCaves location: class server FightCaves = new FightCaves(); ^ 2 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Thanks.
